1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:06,456
Characters, actions, places,
occupations, and events in this series

2
00:00:06,480 --> 00:00:09,216
are fictional and created for
entertainment purposes only.

3
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:13,976
They are not intended to urge or
promote any behavior in the series.

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,239
Viewer discretion is advised.

5
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:17,720
Are you really leaving Prim?

6
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:19,016
Has she ever cared about anyone?

7
00:00:19,040 --> 00:00:20,840
All she cares about is Bambi.

8
00:00:20,880 --> 00:00:23,560
Do you know
that Prim and Min are fighting?

9
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,880
It's because of me.

10
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:27,160
You are nominated
because you two worked together.

11
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,320
Let's go public with our relationship.

12
00:00:28,360 --> 00:00:29,576
Your mom will never let us do that.

13
00:00:29,600 --> 00:00:31,560
We have to admit that we have to choose.

14
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:33,120
But I chose you.

15
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,280
But I chose myself.

16
00:00:47,120 --> 00:00:48,200
Hold on.

17
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,600
Let me adjust her clothes a bit.

18
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:56,200
You can continue now.

19
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,880
I bought snacks.

20
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:09,400
It's for everyone.

21
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,080
- Thank you.
- Please enjoy it.

22
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:14,200
With this great support, we will wrap up
the shooting quickly today.

23
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:16,360
We can wrap it up quickly
if you don't slack off.

24
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,560
Right.

25
00:01:19,080 --> 00:01:20,080
See?

26
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,880
I think we got it.
Let's move to the next look.

27
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,080
Okay, let's move to the next look.

28
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:31,880
Did you forget
that your girlfriend is a model?

29
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:34,680
Why didn't you ask me to model
for your first collection?

30
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:38,080
Before modeling for me,
you should talk to your mom first.

31
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:40,416
Otherwise, she will accuse me
of riding on your coattails.

32
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,479
Ride on my coattails?

33
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:44,400
When you become famous,
I'll ride on your coattails.

34
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,400
Shasha, there are many people here.

35
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,600
Why?

36
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,280
It's normal to kiss my girlfriend.

37
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,360
Did you mess up my face?

38
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:54,039
No, I didn't.

39
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:55,440
Shasha.

40
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,657
There are many people here. Stop it.

41
00:01:56,681 --> 00:01:57,880
I'll get back to work.

42
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,440
Can I have a full body shot?

43
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:03,640
Sure.

44
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,480
Beautiful.

45
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,720
Great.

46
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,280
That's great.

47
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,240
I think it's good.

48
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:14,960
But I want more close-up
and full-body shots for the next look.

49
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,680
Sure.

50
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,680
Where is the next model?

51
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,880
Your model is here.

52
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:30,400
Let's start. I'm ready.

53
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,520
What are you doing?

54
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,200
Your mom will complain to me again.

55
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,360
I don't care. I won't back down.

56
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,600
I will be your muse.

57
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:08,216
Hello.

58
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,280
Hello, Gorya.

59
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:12,000
Praew, are you working here now?

60
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:14,440
No, I'm just a freelancer.

61
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:19,279
Since you two became official,
you are inseparable.

62
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:23,080
Min, is Prim upstairs?

63
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,760
I can't reach her.

64
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,880
I want her to take a look
at my brand's ad.

65
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,480
I can't contact her either.

66
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,800
She hasn't come to work for several days.

67
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:32,696
She has to attend
the award show this evening.

68
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,096
It's likely that she won't attend it.

69
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,680
Prim won't attend the award show!?

70
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,640
But that's her dream.

71
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,000
Yes.

72
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,520
What happened?

73
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,760
I think it's about Bambi.

74
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:44,320
Their relationship is just toxic.

75
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
Is she at her apartment?

76
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,280
I don't know.

77
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:54,056
I sleep over
at Praew's apartment these days.

78
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,360
What's wrong with her?

79
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:58,200
This is the moment
she's been waiting for her whole life.

80
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,800
She can't let her love ruin it.

81
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,280
I don't know what to do with her.

82
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,200
Prim.

83
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,920
Prim.

84
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,680
Prim, why are you such a mess?

85
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,640
Min.

86
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,560
Can you attend
the award show on my behalf?

87
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,080
No.

88
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,480
You are the nominee.
You need to attend it yourself.

89
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,016
I don't want it anymore.

90
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,680
They can give it to anyone.

91
00:05:50,080 --> 00:05:51,280
Prim, get up.

92
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,280
Pull yourself together.

93
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:56,960
Didn't you work hard to get this award?

94
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:02,080
Can I ask you something?

95
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,680
What's going on?

96
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,480
Bambi left.

97
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,480
She left me.

98
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,680
When we got back together,

99
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,760
I promised myself that
I wouldn't be the one who loves more.

100
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,880
I wouldn't change myself for her.

101
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:42,080
I wouldn't expect
this relationship to last long.

102
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,480
But in the end

103
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:49,280
Bambi was good at this.

104
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:55,280
I expressed through my music video and ads

105
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:59,000
that the second-time breakup
wouldn't be as painful as the first time.

106
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,160
In the end,

107
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:04,600
a breakup is always painful.

108
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,880
You can vent out as much as you want.

109
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:14,960
Prim.

110
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,680
You need to pull yourself together.

111
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:21,040
Are you sure…

112
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,760
If you miss the award show,

113
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:26,920
you won't regret it?

114
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,480
You are the leader
of the workaholics club.

115
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:42,360
You're a director who would rather die
than lower your standards at work.

116
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,840
You have a high expectation
of this award, don't you?

117
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:48,760
Don't you want to see with your own eyes
who wins the award?

118
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,200
Yes, I do.

119
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,280
That's it.

120
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:58,000
Forget about your love for a while.

121
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,880
Forget about her.

122
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,880
Just focus on the award.

123
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:07,960
About your hair, makeup, and outfit,
I'll take care of it.

124
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:12,200
Prim, you are my idol.

125
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:15,480
If you win this award,
I'll put you on a pedestal.

126
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:17,560
Stay strong.

127
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:25,000
Don't let the love ruin your dream.

128
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:34,480
But it really hurts.

129
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,559
It hurts.

130
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:04,880
Aren't you going to say goodbye
to your best friend before leaving?

131
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,200
How did you get in here?

132
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,680
I bought a ticket to get in here.

133
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:12,920
I don't want to see you make a mistake.

134
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,560
Did Gorya tell you to come here?

135
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:17,440
Yes.

136
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,280
But I also want to come.

137
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:22,480
Don't try to talk me out of it.

138
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:24,880
I already made up my mind.

139
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,720
Do you think this is a sacrifice?

140
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,400
You are so selfish.

141
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:32,720
This is so cowardly.

142
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,440
You are not the Bambi that I know.

143
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:39,480
Selfish? How?

144
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,280
I did this

145
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:44,120
I left for the sake of the person I love.

146
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,320
Nonsense.

147
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:48,280
If you love her, you should be with her.

148
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:55,400
When we have someone with us as we cry,

149
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:57,400
it feels good.

150
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,880
When we are happy and successful,

151
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:07,280
having someone we love
and care about by our side,

152
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:09,880
it feels so damn good.

153
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:40,200
The agency of the year award goes to…

154
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,600
One More Take.

155
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,440
One day.

156
00:10:56,040 --> 00:10:57,720
Lady Bird will be announced on the stage.

157
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,560
Yes.

158
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,080
One day, it will be our day.

159
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:09,040
Thank you, everyone,
for giving this award to our company.

160
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,200
Thank you very much.

161
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:26,800
The next award is the award
you've been waiting for.

162
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:30,280
The best newcomer director.

163
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,800
This is your time.

164
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:40,360
The best newcomer director goes to…

165
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:59,480
Prim Pariyakorn Rungruengsuk
from Lady Bird.

166
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,200
You made it.

167
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,760
First of all,

168
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:27,240
thank you for this award.

169
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:33,280
There are many people
who helped me win this award.

170
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:38,200
I can't come this far by myself.

171
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:41,280
Many people support me from behind.

172
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:43,880
My family.

173
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,840
My friends,

174
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:50,760
my coworkers and many more.

175
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:53,080
These people,

176
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,280
they help me get where I am today.

177
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,160
I'm not that talented.

178
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:01,600
Sometimes, I feel discouraged.

179
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,280
But there was one person

180
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,000
who took care of me.

181
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:12,280
She made sure that I ate.

182
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:15,880
She made sure that I had enough sleep.

183
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:21,600
She always told me that I did well
when I didn't feel confident.

184
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:25,680
She is the one
I want to share my happiness with.

185
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,880
Today, I want to tell her this.

186
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,320
Hey.

187
00:13:44,640 --> 00:13:45,880
I made it.

188
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:50,400
This award is also yours.

189
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,080
My girlfriend is the best.

190
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:47,400
Prim will come back to work now.

191
00:14:50,520 --> 00:14:54,360
If one day, when you win an award,
I'll cheer you on like this, too.

192
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,680
Don't do it.

193
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:58,800
I like being behind the scenes.

194
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:00,896
If I have to get on stage
and give a speech,

195
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:03,880
I will stumble over my words
and struggle with the speech.

196
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:08,200
You can thank yourself for working hard.

197
00:15:10,760 --> 00:15:11,880
Then

198
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,000
I would have to mention you in my speech.

199
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:18,400
Thank you for being
such a lovely girlfriend.

200
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,800
You always support me.

201
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:25,320
I didn't do that because it's my duty.

202
00:15:25,760 --> 00:15:26,920
I do it because I want to.

203
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:32,640
I think I need to give you a reward.

204
00:15:34,360 --> 00:15:35,360
What reward?

205
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:38,480
A big reward.

206
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:49,960
Bring the award closer to your face.

207
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:53,200
Good.

208
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,080
I've never thought I would win it.

209
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,560
The other nominees are very talented.

210
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:02,080
You are talented too.

211
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:07,080
Next year, you will no longer be
a newcomer director.

212
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:09,280
You will be a veteran director.

213
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:12,800
Prim, can I have your autograph?

214
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,880
I never thought that you would come back.

215
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:19,080
I thought I missed you too much
that I saw your hallucination.

216
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:21,680
I almost left.

217
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:25,280
But in the end,
I realized that I couldn't leave you.

218
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:29,480
I don't want your happiest day

219
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:33,680
to be ruined by my selfishness
disguised as love.

220
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,200
Can I scold you?

221
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:42,440
Yes.

222
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:47,120
Do it.

223
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:50,680
Scold me. I'll listen to it.

224
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:52,800
Do it.

225
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:55,480
No.

226
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:56,840
I won't scold you.

227
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,800
Today is one of my happiest days.

228
00:17:06,560 --> 00:17:08,480
You won't go to New York, right?

229
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:13,359
I may have to go there sometimes.

230
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,400
I saw opportunities for my work there.

231
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:19,880
But

232
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:21,520
I won't move to live there permanently.

233
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,480
What about us?

234
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,800
We are not breaking up, right?

235
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:33,160
That's up to you.

236
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:36,280
All this time,
I made the decision by myself.

237
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:40,080
This time, I'll let you decide.

238
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:47,280
From now on, our relationship
will no longer be on-and-off.

239
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,960
From now on,

240
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:53,080
we will be together forever.

241
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:56,120
No matter how many times
I have to win you over.

242
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,056
Even if we have to have
a long-distance relationship

243
00:17:58,080 --> 00:18:00,720
or I have to go study films there
to be with you,

244
00:18:01,120 --> 00:18:02,480
I'll do it.

245
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,560
Really?

246
00:18:06,120 --> 00:18:07,200
You are so sweet.

247
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:12,040
Close your eyes.

248
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:13,920
Why?

249
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:15,800
I want to give you a reward.

250
00:18:21,760 --> 00:18:22,760
Bambi.

251
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:24,240
Wait a sec.

252
00:18:24,280 --> 00:18:25,800
I'm getting ready.

253
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:37,000
Open your eyes.

254
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:46,000
I think it suits us.

255
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:48,760
Thank you.

256
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:57,280
Let's stay together
to complete our bucket list.

257
00:19:10,360 --> 00:19:11,560
I want more rewards.

258
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,600
Please tell us how you are feeling today.

259
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:24,840
I'm really excited.

260
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:27,216
I came here to cheer on my friend.

261
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:29,280
I'm so happy for her
for winning the award.

262
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,480
Can I ask you a question?

263
00:19:31,760 --> 00:19:34,640
Who is the woman in the photo
you posted the other day?

264
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:38,160
Your mom said she was your stylist,
not your girlfriend.

265
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:40,360
Can you tell us who she is?

266
00:19:40,520 --> 00:19:41,680
That's right. Please tell us.

267
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:44,080
Your mom said you were still single.

268
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:48,280
Why did she say you were still single?

269
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:49,560
Please answer us.

270
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:53,520
I'm not single anymore.

271
00:19:55,600 --> 00:19:56,600
What?

272
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:58,880
Who are you dating?

273
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,080
What do you mean by that?

274
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:06,760
This is Gorya, my girlfriend.

275
00:20:09,120 --> 00:20:11,416
Many girls and boys
will have their hearts broken.

276
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,600
