That's so sweet.

283
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:27,080
When I love someone,
I want everyone to love her too.

284
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,560
You're so sweet.

285
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:33,800
I promise I will work hard as always.

286
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,400
How did you two meet?

287
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,880
How have you been dating?

288
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,216
