289
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:40,176
Please answer us.

290
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,640
How long have you been together?

291
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,760
Please answer us.

292
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:45,480
Please answer us.

293
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,320
Please answer us, Gorya.

294
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:49,360
