295
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,440
At first, she hated me.

296
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:58,880
But this is us now.

297
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:01,080
From haters to

298
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,560
lovers.

299
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:06,240
That's so romantic.

300
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,800
Do you have anything to say?

301
00:21:08,760 --> 00:21:09,800
Please say something.

302
00:21:10,160 --> 00:21:11,560
She is shy.

303
00:21:11,880 --> 00:21:13,880
You can ask me.
I'll answer your questions.

304
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:16,616
Please be nice to Gorya.

305
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:17,400
Sure.

306
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:20,520
We will love your girlfriend
just like we love you.

307
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,200
Please tell us if you have good news.

308
00:21:23,480 --> 00:21:26,800
(I'm not single anymore.)

309
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,680
(This is Gorya, my girlfriend.)

310
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:34,720
I'm sorry.

311
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:37,080
But your card is declined.

312
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:42,360
How is that possible?
My card has a high credit limit.

313
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,480
Go try again.

314
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:46,040
I've tried several times,
but the payment doesn't go through.

315
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,480
Do you have another card?

316
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:50,880
No, this is the only card I have.

317
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:54,080
But my daughter set the credit limit high.

318
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,080
I canceled your card.

319
00:21:57,600 --> 00:21:59,840
Sha, what is going on?

320
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,480
I canceled your card.

321
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,040
Your spending is too much. I can't pay it.

322
00:22:05,440 --> 00:22:08,200
I work hard for myself,
not for anyone else.

323
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:11,680
How can you say that to me?

324
00:22:12,280 --> 00:22:14,080
You have never acted like this before.

325
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:19,880
Since you are dating Gorya,
you have changed a lot.

326
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:21,280
That's right.

327
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,880
I learned to love myself because of Gorya.

328
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:26,600
Love yourself?

329
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:29,400
That's why the news about your relationship
is all over social media.

330
00:22:29,720 --> 00:22:32,960
Who will want to hire you after this?

331
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:36,280
She is scamming you.

332
00:22:36,560 --> 00:22:39,560
When she gets everything that she wants,
she will leave you.

333
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:40,920
Just like other girls did to you.

334
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:43,960
I think it's you who is scamming her.

335
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:46,240
I've never wanted anything from her.

336
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:49,680
If she decides to retire from the business
and has nothing left,

337
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:51,480
I will still love her.

338
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,120
What about you?

339
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:56,000
If she had nothing left,

340
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:58,200
