343
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:09,000
You can't fire her. She works for me.

344
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:12,200
How can you choose her, a girlfriend
whom you're with for a few days,

345
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,240
