346
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:14,480
What about you?

347
00:23:15,320 --> 00:23:18,080
You got married and moved to live abroad.

348
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:20,440
It's because
you needed to stay here to work.

349
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:25,280
If I didn't leave you,
you wouldn't have become a celebrity.

350
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:28,600
Have you ever asked me
if I wanted to do it?

351
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:33,280
Do you know what I went through
to get where I am today?

352
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:40,400
But it is worth it, isn't it?

353
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:43,200
Let bygones be bygones.

354
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,680
Everyone has problems.

355
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:53,720
MRS. EMIKA JIRUNTANON
3 MILLION BAHT

356
00:23:59,920 --> 00:24:01,200
