360
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:09,080
We will live separate lives.

361
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:12,856
But I will wire your allowance
like I used to.

362
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,960
I'll think of it as repayment
for giving birth to me.

363
00:24:36,080 --> 00:24:37,080
Do I look good?

364
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,040
Of course.

365
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,680
Let's take photos.

366
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,480
How do I look?

367
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,920
You look good.

368
00:24:43,920 --> 00:24:45,680
Let's practice your smile.

369
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:49,936
We are taking a family portrait today.

370
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:51,600
Why did you bring your friend with you?

371
00:24:52,200 --> 00:24:55,160
Where is the person
who will take photos for us?

372
00:24:57,280 --> 00:24:58,880
She is the camerawoman

373
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:01,040
and my girlfriend.

374
00:25:10,240 --> 00:25:11,360
What are you talking about?

375
00:25:11,760 --> 00:25:12,760
I don't want to hear it.

376
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:14,280
You will change your mind.

377
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:16,680
You just haven't found a good man yet.

378
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:18,800
Why don't you get back with Park?

379
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,000
Dad.

380
00:25:20,040 --> 00:25:21,120
I won't change my mind.

381
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:23,880
I don't know what the future holds.

382
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,080
But she is the person I love.

383
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:28,360
I want to share my future with her.

384
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:33,640
I want you and Mom to accept her
the same way you accepted Park.

385
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,680
Why didn't you teach your daughter?

386
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:44,760
How can you let her become a homo?

387
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:47,520
Uncle, you should spend your time
teaching your son.

388
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:48,960
He graduated several years ago.

389
00:25:49,320 --> 00:25:51,040
But he still lives off you.

390
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:58,600
Do you want your daughter to be like Joo?

391
00:25:59,120 --> 00:26:00,640
What's wrong with being like Aunt Joo?

392
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,000
So what?

393
00:26:02,320 --> 00:26:04,800
You can cut me off if you want.

394
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:08,000
I'd rather be with someone
who accepts me for who I am.

395
00:26:08,120 --> 00:26:09,120
Let's go, Praew.

396
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,480
Min, don't go.

397
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:13,800
Let's take photos together first.

398
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:18,600
I'm sure you chose this
for your own happiness.

399
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,560
You are still our daughter.

400
00:26:23,320 --> 00:26:24,560
If this makes you happy,

401
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,760
