402
00:26:31,280 --> 00:26:32,280
Am I right, Dad?

403
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:45,040
Praew, can you take photos for us?

404
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:47,360
And you should take photos with us too.

405
00:26:48,280 --> 00:26:49,080
Sure.

406
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:51,000
I'll set up the camera first.

407
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,400
Come on.

408
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:55,176
The world has changed so much.

409
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,160
I can't keep up with the changes.

410
00:26:57,560 --> 00:27:00,480
Since you two are together,
you should take good care of each other.

411
00:27:01,800 --> 00:27:02,960
Thank you, Grandma.

412
00:27:03,320 --> 00:27:04,800
You look prettiest today.

413
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:07,520
That's good.

414
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:09,000
It's like I have another daughter.

415
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:13,680
Are you ready?

416
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:16,480
One, two, three.

417
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,680
One more time.

418
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:23,200
One, two, three.

419
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:28,800
Praew, come and take a picture with us.

420
00:27:45,920 --> 00:27:47,800
I won a big award.

421
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:52,200
Was it decided by popular vote
or something else?

422
00:27:52,800 --> 00:27:54,560
It was based solely on her work.

423
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:56,600
Prim is highly wanted.

424
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:58,200
Many people want to work with her.

425
00:27:58,360 --> 00:27:59,800
She is going to make a movie soon.

426
00:28:00,800 --> 00:28:02,600
You should let your sister answer it.

427
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:05,040
You answered everything
as if you were her PR rep.

428
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:07,000
I'm just excited for her.

429
00:28:09,680 --> 00:28:11,560
I'm proud of you.

430
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:16,280
You not only take care of our family
but also achieve your dream.

431
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:19,440
You don't need to worry
about your sister or me anymore.

432
00:28:19,480 --> 00:28:21,040
Just think about your own happiness.

433
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:23,800
My sister is so talented.

434
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,280
Come on. Let's hug.

435
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,800
- I'm so happy.
- I'm so happy for you.

436
00:28:32,880 --> 00:28:33,960
I'm so happy for you.

437
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,640
I love you, Mom.

438
00:28:35,720 --> 00:28:36,440
I love you.

439
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:37,800
I love you too.

440
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:41,000
Bambi, come here and hug her together.

441
00:28:41,280 --> 00:28:42,656
We are both her supporters.

442
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:43,320
Come on.

443
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:44,400
It's okay.

444
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:45,720
I'm still an outsider.

445
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:49,000
One day, you will be a part of this family.

446
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:50,120
Come on. Come here.

447
00:28:50,240 --> 00:28:51,160
Come on.

448
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,720
You can't take your words back later.

449
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,480
Don't break up again.

450
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:01,960
We won't.

451
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,960
We will be together and get married.

452
00:29:05,040 --> 00:29:07,200
Are you only saying this
in front of your mom?

453
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,560
Your designs look great.

454
00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:16,280
They are unique.

455
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:19,360
See? I told you.

456
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:24,400
This is a good chance for you
to invest in a new designer.

457
00:29:25,080 --> 00:29:26,680
