458
00:29:28,120 --> 00:29:30,120
Gorya's designs are amazing.

459
00:29:30,840 --> 00:29:31,840
Mom, look.

460
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:34,920
If you turn down this opportunity,
you will regret it.

461
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:37,360
When will you get
an opportunity like this again?

462
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:39,800
They look amazing.

463
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:47,920
Okay.

464
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:50,960
Deal.

465
00:29:51,680 --> 00:29:53,280
I'll wait to see your final designs.

466
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:57,520
Are you serious?

467
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,280
Don't disappoint me.

468
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,840
Thank you. Thank you so much.

469
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:04,200
I won't disappoint you.

470
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:08,360
I guarantee this is a moonshot.

471
00:30:11,840 --> 00:30:13,600
You will make
hundreds of millions from it.

472
00:30:14,080 --> 00:30:15,160
Stop it.

473
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,160
I told you.

474
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:23,560
My mom would definitely buy it.

475
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,280
Why are you helping me?

476
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:26,800
Because

477
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:30,600
I want to be your friend.

478
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,160
So you are trying to buy me?

479
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:36,880
Why would I need to buy a friend?

480
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:40,360
I see it as an investment.

481
00:30:44,320 --> 00:30:47,560
This will be a smart investment.

482
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:50,600
It will make profits.

483
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:53,240
I'll make a lot of money for your mom.

484
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:57,160
I will also give you advice about Prim.

485
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,080
So we are now friends, right?

486
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:04,120
I don't need to be polite
with you anymore, do I?

487
00:31:09,560 --> 00:31:10,560
Sure.

488
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:12,760
Fine by me.

489
00:31:15,280 --> 00:31:16,280
Deal.

490
00:31:18,280 --> 00:31:19,280
Deal.

491
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,480
Bambi.

492
00:31:22,080 --> 00:31:23,120
Gorya.

493
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:33,480
Are you applying for a job?

494
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,360
Yes.

495
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:38,136
I sent my application to many companies.

496
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,880
But none of them contacted me.

497
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,120
I guess I have to do everything by myself.

498
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:43,960
Shooting and editing videos.

499
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:46,560
But the salary is only 15,000 baht.

500
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:49,040
After paying the rent,
I'll have nothing left.

501
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:52,280
Why don't you work for me?

502
00:31:52,520 --> 00:31:53,880
I'll pay you well.

503
00:32:02,320 --> 00:32:04,480
Min, it's tickling.

504
00:32:06,160 --> 00:32:09,680
You don't need to pay me.
I'll do it anyway.

505
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,800
What do you mean?

506
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:16,680
I mean, you should work for my company.

507
00:32:17,080 --> 00:32:19,360
You can take photos and videos for us.

508
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:24,560
Work?

509
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:26,400
Are you interested?

510
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:28,360
Prim likes your work.

511
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,240
No.

512
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:33,160
I'll keep looking.

513
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:35,376
I don't want people to think
I got this job because of you.

514
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,496
Why do you need to care about it?

515
00:32:36,520 --> 00:32:37,520
Just ignore it.

516
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:40,680
I'll think about it.

517
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:44,280
Okay, okay. Fine.

518
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,480
Don't stress about it too much.

519
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:49,600
I'm right here.

520
00:32:50,080 --> 00:32:53,720
I can afford to support my girlfriend.

521
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:10,680
Are you okay now?

522
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,960
Yes.

523
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:15,600
I wanted to say that to her
for a long time.

524
00:33:15,720 --> 00:33:17,080
But I didn't dare to do it.

525
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:19,080
I feel relieved after saying it.

526
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:23,360
But there won't be another problem, right?

527
00:33:23,760 --> 00:33:26,280
She won't say she is a victim

528
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,160
or that I'm manipulating you.

529
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:30,840
No. Did you watch too many movies?

530
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,000
Who knows what will happen?

531
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,696
It may happen if she runs out of money.

532
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,760
Are you serious?

533
00:33:37,400 --> 00:33:38,480
No.

534
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:40,600
If she does that,

535
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:43,680
she knows she will never get
a single penny from me.

536
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:45,880
That's true.

537
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:49,280
She wouldn't cut off her own lifeline.

538
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:56,680
But no matter what happens,

539
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:59,160
I will always be by your side.

540
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,600
I believe you.

541
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:03,160
Look at how you scolded her.

542
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,680
I was worked up.

543
00:34:07,040 --> 00:34:08,199
I get it.

544
00:34:09,639 --> 00:34:13,199
Did you see our news on social media?

545
00:34:13,679 --> 00:34:15,320
They say we look good together.

546
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:19,520
You wrote the comment yourself,
didn't you?

547
00:34:20,159 --> 00:34:22,199
No, many people left similar comments.

548
00:34:22,679 --> 00:34:23,880
I told you

549
00:34:24,600 --> 00:34:26,199
we are perfect for each other.

550
00:34:28,800 --> 00:34:30,000
This is unbelievable.

551
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:33,600
When I decided to go public
with our relationship,

552
00:34:34,120 --> 00:34:35,880
I just wanted to have
a simple life with you.

553
00:34:36,239 --> 00:34:37,960
I wanted us to go outside without hiding.

554
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,800
We can go to a mall.

555
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:43,080
I can hold your hand in public.

556
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:46,360
I can kiss you.

557
00:34:46,760 --> 00:34:49,280
I can peck you like this.

558
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,080
You can do it now.

559
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,080
From now on, when we come here,

560
00:34:58,920 --> 00:35:00,800
we will no longer have a surprise guest.

561
00:35:02,400 --> 00:35:03,880
It's not bad to have one.

562
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,280
It's kind of exciting.

563
00:35:42,520 --> 00:35:44,400
This wedding is so Ant and Fa.

564
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,560
They are cute.

565
00:35:47,240 --> 00:35:49,400
They went through a lot together.

566
00:35:49,960 --> 00:35:51,080
Just like you and me.

567
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:55,200
Here they are.

568
00:36:03,560 --> 00:36:05,080
To tell you the truth,

569
00:36:06,680 --> 00:36:10,200
I never thought I would get married.

570
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:15,480
I thought it was not necessary.

571
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,440
But…

572
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:21,880
When I met Fa,

573
00:36:25,120 --> 00:36:26,560
I changed my mind.

574
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,560
I want to get married.

575
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:32,400
I want to tell everyone

576
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:35,400
how lucky I am to have her as my partner.

577
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,880
Thank you, everyone,
for attending our wedding.

578
00:36:45,520 --> 00:36:48,520
Thank you for being with me when I smile.

579
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:55,320
Thank you for being with me
when I bawl my eyes out.

580
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,680
You guys are important to me,

581
00:37:02,080 --> 00:37:03,640
but not as important as my girlfriend.

582
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:09,480
If I didn't go through a hard time,

583
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:15,680
I would never know how important it is
to have someone by my side.

584
00:37:18,680 --> 00:37:22,000
I never thought love was perfect.

585
00:37:23,720 --> 00:37:25,360
Our life is not a romantic movie.

586
00:37:26,160 --> 00:37:28,280
Not every day is romantic.

587
00:37:29,600 --> 00:37:33,080
One day,
when something bad happens to me.

588
00:37:34,080 --> 00:37:38,000
If I have someone by my side,

589
00:37:39,200 --> 00:37:41,280
someone I can share my story with,

590
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:43,240
that is good enough.

591
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,080
Okay, that's it.

592
00:37:58,000 --> 00:37:59,080
Let's stop here.

593
00:37:59,920 --> 00:38:01,456
Otherwise, I'll cry and ruin my makeup.

594
00:38:01,480 --> 00:38:04,440
Okay, one, two, three.

595
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:52,280
Hello, guests. May I have your attention?

596
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:57,600
Today, I'll represent the guests
to say something to Ant and Fa.

597
00:38:58,520 --> 00:39:02,200
For me, you are…

598
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,000
My friends,

599
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:06,160
my big sisters.

600
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:09,280
You scold me, so I will regain my senses.

601
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:11,880
You also give me advice.

602
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:20,360
You make me believe that my love can work.

603
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,880
You also make me believe

604
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,680
that no matter what happens,

605
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:31,600
the most important thing is

606
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:36,080
as long as we trust each other,

607
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:38,800
we can get through anything together.

608
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,280
Please raise your glass

609
00:39:44,920 --> 00:39:48,080
and drink to celebrate Ant and Fa.

610
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,360
Cheers.

611
00:39:56,520 --> 00:40:00,200
It wouldn't be me if I only gave a speech.

612
00:40:00,640 --> 00:40:04,160
Today, I prepared a surprise for you.

613
00:40:04,680 --> 00:40:07,760
Please welcome Krystal.

614
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:36,880
♪ So many stories to tell ♪

615
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:39,216
♪ So many nights by myself ♪

616
00:40:39,240 --> 00:40:41,200
♪ The heat and the cold ♪

617
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:44,040
♪ That we both have gone through ♪

618
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:47,400
♪ Thousands in the crowd ♪

619
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,896
♪ But nobody at all ♪

620
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:52,880
♪ Who could ever know ♪

621
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:56,200
♪ My heart like you do ♪

622
00:40:56,720 --> 00:41:00,760
♪ Every answer to my question ♪

623
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:06,360
♪ Everything I'd searched for ♪

624
00:41:06,520 --> 00:41:08,960
♪ In the moments ♪

625
00:41:09,240 --> 00:41:11,640
♪ In the seasons ♪

626
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:16,160
♪ All led me to you ♪

627
00:41:16,200 --> 00:41:18,880
♪ I'm forever yours ♪

628
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:21,760
♪ Only you, it's true ♪

629
00:41:22,200 --> 00:41:26,760
♪ All my life and all my heart
belong to you ♪

630
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:29,360
♪ You're the one ♪

631
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:32,120
♪ Standing here before me ♪

632
00:41:32,480 --> 00:41:35,880
♪ When I'm awake and in my dreams ♪

633
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:40,200
♪ I'm so glad that it is you ♪

634
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,400
I never imagined

635
00:41:41,720 --> 00:41:45,280
that you would dance with me
in public like this.

636
00:41:46,400 --> 00:41:48,040
I have nothing to worry about anymore.

637
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,120
And

638
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,080
I am now sure.

639
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:54,840
Sure about what?

640
00:41:56,800 --> 00:42:00,280
I'm sure

641
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:03,000
that we can make it work.

642
00:42:04,520 --> 00:42:06,320
Just like other couples in this wedding.

643
00:42:07,080 --> 00:42:10,480
Are you thinking about marrying me?

644
00:42:11,120 --> 00:42:12,920
But I'm not in a stable place in life yet.

645
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,440
Hold on.

646
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:16,160
I'm not thinking that far.

647
00:42:17,880 --> 00:42:21,560
Just waking up and going to bed with you,

648
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,760
it already makes me happy.

649
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:26,880
Okay.

650
00:42:27,320 --> 00:42:29,800
But I'm not totally against
the idea of us getting married.

651
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:31,880
I just want to live my life for a while first.

652
00:42:32,520 --> 00:42:34,160
Let's take it slowly.

653
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:36,720
Yes.

654
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:39,400
♪ I'm forever yours ♪

655
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:42,360
♪ Only you, it's true ♪

656
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:48,600
The former straight girl is being too PDA.

657
00:42:49,960 --> 00:42:51,760
She's getting shy.

658
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:56,440
♪ When I'm awake and in my dreams ♪

659
00:42:56,560 --> 00:43:00,760
♪ I'm so glad that it is you ♪

660
00:43:03,680 --> 00:43:07,800
♪ I'm forever yours ♪

661
00:43:35,920 --> 00:43:36,920
What's going on?

662
00:43:38,480 --> 00:43:39,680
I just want to hold you.

663
00:43:40,760 --> 00:43:43,640
I'm touched by Ant's speech.

664
00:43:43,680 --> 00:43:45,520
I felt like I was listening to our story.

665
00:43:46,960 --> 00:43:47,960
That's true.

666
00:43:48,640 --> 00:43:51,160
We've been on and off several times.

667
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:56,400
This time, can we make it
until we get married like them?

668
00:43:56,960 --> 00:43:58,400
Of course.

669
00:44:03,560 --> 00:44:04,600
I believe you.

670
00:44:05,240 --> 00:44:07,000
We will be together for a long time.

671
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:09,920
But…

672
00:44:11,080 --> 00:44:16,040
Can you put up with my self-centeredness
for the rest of your life?

673
00:44:19,240 --> 00:44:20,280
I think

674
00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:23,200
one day you will reach your limit.

675
00:44:24,600 --> 00:44:25,760
Are you sure you can do it?

676
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:31,200
Are you sure you can put up with
my difficult temperament and workaholism?

677
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:33,480
If you can do it, I can too.

678
00:44:36,880 --> 00:44:41,600
What if I am the only girl you can hold
for the rest of your life?

679
00:44:42,480 --> 00:44:44,480
I won't let you hold other girls anymore.

680
00:44:46,040 --> 00:44:47,480
Sure.

681
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:51,000
I will hold you tight
and will never let you go.

682
00:44:59,320 --> 00:45:00,320
What if?

683
00:45:11,080 --> 00:45:12,880
Will you be okay?

684
00:45:15,640 --> 00:45:17,960
If I am the only girl you can kiss.

685
00:45:21,560 --> 00:45:22,960
It will be more than okay.

686
00:45:24,320 --> 00:45:25,840
It will be my pleasure.

687
00:45:37,560 --> 00:45:39,880
You and I are not 100 percent good.

688
00:45:41,200 --> 00:45:42,760
That's why we are together.

689
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:48,040
Just look at you, I can tell what you want.

690
00:45:49,840 --> 00:45:51,040
So…

691
00:45:52,720 --> 00:45:55,880
You know what I want right now.

692
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:00,440
What?

693
00:46:01,840 --> 00:46:04,560
I have a new wish on my bucket list.

694
00:46:05,800 --> 00:46:08,880
I want to do something exciting like this
for some time.

695
00:46:42,320 --> 00:46:43,320
Shasha, come on.

696
00:46:57,240 --> 00:46:58,680
What are you doing?

697
00:46:59,440 --> 00:47:00,720
You took me by surprise.

698
00:47:00,760 --> 00:47:01,880
I looked startled.

699
00:47:02,920 --> 00:47:07,080
Alright, I will slowly kiss you.

700
00:47:09,520 --> 00:47:10,600
Stop it.

701
00:47:11,200 --> 00:47:12,296
We started our relationship this way.

702
00:47:12,320 --> 00:47:14,520
So we kind of skipped
the romantic moments.

703
00:47:15,160 --> 00:47:19,000
Can't you do something cute and sweet?

704
00:47:19,960 --> 00:47:21,480
Cute and sweet?

705
00:47:22,200 --> 00:47:23,920
But you like me the way I am, don't you?

706
00:47:24,440 --> 00:47:25,440
Yes.

707
00:47:25,800 --> 00:47:28,840
But we need to have different sides
to make people want to get to know you.

708
00:47:29,880 --> 00:47:32,680
What if you get to know me
and find something you don't like about me?

709
00:47:35,200 --> 00:47:36,200
It's not a big deal.

710
00:47:36,640 --> 00:47:39,880
Because there might be things
you don't like about me, too.

711
00:47:40,440 --> 00:47:41,440
Am I right?

712
00:47:42,520 --> 00:47:43,520
No.

713
00:47:43,920 --> 00:47:45,400
I like everything about you.

714
00:47:46,240 --> 00:47:47,280
Nonsense.

715
00:47:48,440 --> 00:47:51,280
Teach me how to do a cute pose.

716
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:55,080
Cute pose like this.

717
00:47:55,760 --> 00:47:56,880
Don't do this.

718
00:47:58,080 --> 00:47:59,080
No.

719
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:00,760
This is hard.

720
00:48:01,760 --> 00:48:02,480
Okay.

721
00:48:02,640 --> 00:48:04,000
I can do it for you.

722
00:48:06,080 --> 00:48:07,080
I press here, right?

723
00:48:18,520 --> 00:48:20,680
Didn't you say you like cute poses?

724
00:48:22,240 --> 00:48:27,880
Since we started this way,
we should stick with it.

725
00:48:30,440 --> 00:48:31,440
Sure.

726
00:48:32,040 --> 00:48:34,680
I'm good at doing that.

727
00:49:06,000 --> 00:49:07,480
Now they are married.

728
00:49:08,000 --> 00:49:09,160
What will they do next?

729
00:49:10,400 --> 00:49:11,880
Is this the ending?

730
00:49:13,840 --> 00:49:15,880
They might find a new goal.

731
00:49:17,280 --> 00:49:19,200
They might find a way to have kids.

732
00:49:19,880 --> 00:49:21,880
That's the typical path
for most straight couples.

733
00:49:23,360 --> 00:49:24,600
It's not about sexuality.

734
00:49:25,160 --> 00:49:29,680
Some want to get married and have kids.

735
00:49:30,120 --> 00:49:31,200
Some want to stay single.

736
00:49:32,600 --> 00:49:35,880
As long as they can choose what they want
and don't need to follow the norms.

737
00:49:36,440 --> 00:49:38,080
Their life, their choice.

738
00:49:38,680 --> 00:49:39,680
That's right.

739
00:49:39,800 --> 00:49:42,080
I want to travel around the world
without any plans.

740
00:49:45,280 --> 00:49:46,720
My girlfriend is rich. Period.

741
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:47,600
Period.

742
00:49:47,760 --> 00:49:48,760
Can we do that too?

743
00:49:49,440 --> 00:49:50,960
I'll work hard to earn money.

744
00:49:52,920 --> 00:49:53,920
Wait.

745
00:49:54,560 --> 00:49:56,600
This song would be perfect
for a fashion show.

746
00:49:57,720 --> 00:49:59,800
They probably chose this song
for our model.

747
00:50:00,240 --> 00:50:02,680
Show us your catwalk.

748
00:50:03,400 --> 00:50:04,400
I dare you.

749
00:50:05,120 --> 00:50:07,920
If I do it, you all have to do it too.

750
00:50:08,040 --> 00:50:09,040
What?

751
00:50:09,160 --> 00:50:10,160
Come on.

752
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:11,520
Give it a try.

753
00:50:30,280 --> 00:50:31,560
Gorya, go for it.

754
00:50:44,520 --> 00:50:46,360
Bambi, go for it.

755
00:50:46,840 --> 00:50:47,840
Sweetie.

756
00:50:48,040 --> 00:50:49,960
Sweetie, bring it on.

757
00:51:03,160 --> 00:51:04,600
Prim, Prim, Prim.

758
00:51:12,440 --> 00:51:13,680
Who's next?

759
00:51:14,120 --> 00:51:15,480
Go.

760
00:51:20,440 --> 00:51:22,880
You need to act lively like teenagers.

761
00:51:24,520 --> 00:51:25,520
Let's roll, Praew.
